{"tid":2411328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店另推「健康馬」供食客填寫 　店主：政府要留難都冇辦法","createTime":"2021-02-17T08:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T11:15:44.000Z","uid":271829,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fd80311fd9fe12a19f25cb9d10b244de67e715","tid":2411328,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ILfkSmhIx1NeVZFbBOeUFQb4FPw=/6591x4394/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RD2UHIP72JGPJBELZS62G6BE2A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FILfkSmhIx1NeVZFbBOeUFQb4FPw%3D%2F6591x4394%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRD2UHIP72JGPJBELZS62G6BE2A.JPG&h=04eb2f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃店「開餐 Dine Inn 」負責人Eddy表示，客人填寫資料卡後投入密封資料箱，31日後便會銷毀。 本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n武漢肺炎第四波疫情逐漸緩和，政府宣佈明日食肆（18日）恢復晚市堂食，每檯可由2人增至4人等，惟光顧市民要強制掃「安心出行」二維碼（QR code）或留下姓名、到訪時間及電話等個人資料，食肆需保留資料31日。黃店「開餐 Dine Inn 」負責人Eddy 稱已經預備資料卡，客人填寫後自行投入密封資料箱，保留31日後便會銷毀，強調不會要求客人使用QR code。他坦言，有心理準備將有執法人員巡查，惟依足政府宣佈的措施，「佢要留難，佢要告，我都冇辦法 。」<br />\n<br />\n黃店「開餐 Dine Inn 」負責人Eddy表示，客人填寫資料卡後投入密封資料箱，31日後便會銷毀。 本報記者攝<br />\n《蘋果》今早到開餐的灣仔分店，店外貼有「安心出行」的QR code，而下方則畫有「健康馬」的圖案，上方則貼上「不可一不可再，向『掃碼』說不」的標語。店內亦貼有文宣，談及「安心岀行」程式的隱憂。<br />\n<br />\n「唔好佢進一步 你退十步」<br />\n網上近日岀現爭論，有人認為黃店跟從政府政策，要求客人留資料，等同「跪低」，亦有黃店已選擇放棄晚市堂食，寧願繼續捱，也不想遵從新政策。<br />\nEddy認為，這個情況如同《國安法》實施時，黃店內部份文宣因違法而不能繼續張貼，「如果繼續死撐，我寧願犯法都要貼岀嚟，係咪嗰啲先係真黃店？」他說店內仍貼有文宣，不會完全配合政府要求食客使用「安心出行」，「佢進一步，你咪退一步，唔好吓吓話佢進一步，你退十步。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/UDLO7D55BNH43MIFQHFGYQK6VA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FUDLO7D55BNH43MIFQHFGYQK6VA%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN26Cfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=ae387194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FUDLO7D55BNH43MIFQHFGYQK6VA%2F&h=9298ace7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/UDLO7D55BNH43MIFQHFGYQK6VA/</a>"},{"pid":"0917e84945101a17c8ed11eba78916e72f8c15d8","tid":2411328,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c077a1e4979b13e081a52d0a969f4b743f3ffc3","tid":2411328,"uid":37505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"佢進一步，你咪退一步，唔好吓吓話佢進一步，你退十步"},{"pid":"6ca10435434df0dc32abbcdfdbbe0344a7efada2","tid":2411328,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}